description: Number of Go games with n moves.
comments: No value up to a(5) in this sequence is prime. The semiprimes in the sequence begin: 362 = 2 * 181, 6046709375131 = 19 * 318247861849. [Jonathan Vos Post, Apr 02 2011]
references: N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
Cho, Chikun, Go: A Complete Introduction to the Game, Kiseido Publishers, Tokyo, 1997.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
